{"tid":1484583,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民陣 不如下次試下咁報參加人數","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T15:00:55.000Z","uid":7971,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3421ecd31e13e73f0abbe1a0e1bc659f3fdc08","tid":1484583,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"用818今日為例:<br />\n<br />\n維園 到銅鑼灣一帶 今日人數係超過170萬人次<br />\n由於 鵝頸橋以外未有義工安排計算<br />\n但我哋相信 灣仔 金鐘 中環 北角 炮台山 一帶 <br />\n嘅參加者 因交通同路面擠塞 未能進入集會<br />\n但佢哋都係持同一訴求<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">所以民陣<span style=\"color: red;\">推算</span> 維園集會<br />\n連埋上述地區嘅參加者係達250萬人次</span><br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n你報咗170萬就係170萬 <br />\n蘋果通知都係第一時間寫咗 逾170萬<br />\n我知主辦單位 有佢嘅擔心<br />\n但如果 我哋明明真係有超過依一個人數<br />\n點解又為持守一個 數字上嘅道德枷鎖呢？"},{"pid":"dbe6e2155167bbf6462922326e54cd5d9b73c060","tid":1484583,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e410c39aecc17939befe334f7cb5fd04cd79863","tid":1484583,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c39d3530113605516d04749c1236108e205bd62","tid":1484583,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5f0134204afa8b346eec6c13ac0dae811b82df2","tid":1484583,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:54:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12fce285b5945129e0c70de737b3ebf460e88a6f","tid":1484583,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9b29acb2a7134dc87f7c74fe795a9d12a29a9e11","tid":1484583,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5f0134204afa8b346eec6c13ac0dae811b82df2","tid":1484583,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c39d3530113605516d04749c1236108e205bd62","tid":1484583,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"